<sect2 id="structure">
<title>Structure of your Document</title>

<para>With the toolbar or the
<menuchoice><guimenu>Latex</guimenu><guisubmenu>Sectionning</guisubmenu></menuchoice>
menu, you can insert the title of a section or of a paragraph with a
dialog box.  The <guilabel>Structure</guilabel> view is automatically
updated.  While clicking on one item in the
<guilabel>Structure</guilabel> view, the cursor is placed on the
corresponding line in the editor.</para>

<note><para>For file names, it is necessary to double click.  To work
with &kile; all your files must be located in the same directory as
your main document.</para></note>

